Package: buncker
Version: 0.5.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-cryptography (>= 41.0)
Maintainer: Romain G. <buncker@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Offline Docker registry for air-gapped environments
 Buncker is an offline OCI-compliant registry daemon that serves
 Docker images in air-gapped networks. It uses AES-256-GCM encrypted
 USB transfers with BIP-39 mnemonic pairing for secure image delivery.
Homepage: https://github.com/Rwx-G/Buncker
